To get the platform or tool to run your program in sublime text editor : or to run your program

Enter :  ctrl + b

To get list of programs you already ran or writting in sublime  :

Enter : ctrl + p

TO check which groups you are there in your system (ex :whether you are in the list of sudo users):

$ groups

to check you are an sudo user

$ sudo -v
